short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Desk Web Dialer allows you to dial numbers from websites using CyDesk

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Desk Web Dialer will find phone numbers on the web page you are viewing and highlight them
It will provide an icon there to allow you to click on it and dial that number from CyDesk
